# Squad Routing Rules
# Injected by L5 when routing keywords detected

Route tasks to the correct persona based on task type:
- Research/VOC/avatar/competitors -> Vox (@researcher) model:sonnet
- Ads spy/scale score/patterns -> Cipher (@miner) model:sonnet
- Briefing/HELIX/MUP/MUS -> Atlas (@briefer) model:opus
- VSL/leads production -> Echo (@vsl) model:opus
- Landing page production -> Forge (@lp) model:sonnet
- Creative/ads production -> Scout (@creative) model:sonnet
- Email/generic production -> Blade (@producer) model:sonnet
- Validation/review/scores -> Hawk (@critic) model:sonnet
All subagents MUST use subagent_type: "general-purpose" for MCP access.
Agent instructions at ~/.claude/agents/{name}.md — read before executing.
